498
00:23:07.987 --> 00:23:09.182
And I'm Felicia.

499
00:23:09.855 --> 00:23:11.448
Great! Yeah. I knew it.

500
00:23:11.523 --> 00:23:13.458
All hot internet women are guys!

501
