and I are friends.

509
00:23:35.714 --> 00:23:37.546
I just wanna talk
to him for a minute.

510
00:23:37.616 --> 00:23:39.676
So how's it goin'. you good?
- Yeah.

511
00:23:40.920 --> 00:23:42.115
Hey! Whoa!

512
