win enough to pay everybody back.

520
00:24:16.088 --> 00:24:17.920
What'd he say.
you've got till Monday?

521
00:24:17.990 --> 00:24:20.459
Yeah. he did. but
see. the thing is.

522
00:24:20.526 --> 00:24:23.621
I'm a better player than
he is. I am much better.

523
00:24:23.696 --> 00:24:25.665
And yet he bent
you over his knee

524
