front of the whole class.

525
00:24:27.933 --> 00:24:29.595
But he shouldn't have!

526
00:24:29.668 --> 00:24:32.968
I just... I just gotta
figure out how he did it.

527
00:24:33.472 --> 00:24:34.906
Look. Brandon. it's simple.

528
00:24:34.974 --> 00:24:37.385
You go to your dad and convince
him to give you your job back.

529
00:24:37.409 --> 00:24:39.935
And then you figure out a way to
pay this Berger back his money.

530
00:24:40.012 --> 00:24:41.878
Yeah. that sounds really great.

531
00:24:41.947 --> 00:24:44.075
