You have no idea
what that's like.

534
00:24:49.088 --> 00:24:52.422
Look. here's some brutal truth.

535
00:24:52.491 --> 00:24:55.086
We're the only reasons
you're not in jail. or worse.

536
00:24:55.160 --> 00:24:56.253
Your dad's done.

537
00:24:56.328 --> 00:25:00.129
It took someone cashing in a very
old favor to get us involved at all.

538
00:25:00.199 --> 00:25:03.931
Now. you are not gonna be able to
play your way out of this hole. baby boy!

539
00:25:04.003 --> 00:25:07.667
