00:30:30.162 --> 00:30:33.291
You say tomato. I say to-mah-to.

641
00:30:33.365 --> 00:30:34.594
Cha-changa.

642
00:30:34.933 --> 00:30:36.333
The Indian casino?

643
00:30:36.401 --> 00:30:37.869
Cha-ching!

644
00:30:37.936 --> 00:30:40.132
Damn it! You were right. Henry.

645
00:30:40.505 --> 00:30:41.505
How's that?

646
00:30:41.573 --> 00:30:45.533
Maybe getting the police involved
is the only way to get his attention.

647
