656
00:31:11.203 --> 00:31:12.671
he's gonna lose

657
00:31:19.544 --> 00:31:20.739
big!

658
00:31:21.713 --> 00:31:23.477
Not with my money he's not.

659
00:31:28.120 --> 00:31:29.179
Let's go. Oh. God.

660
00:31:29.254 --> 00:31:30.698
We're outta here.
No. Dad. Dad. I can't.

661
