video of you looting my safe?

663
00:31:33.925 --> 00:31:35.621
I know. I'm sorry
about all that.

664
00:31:35.694 --> 00:31:36.889
No. Brandon. Let's go.

665
00:31:36.962 --> 00:31:39.659
No. Dad. Dad. I'm in more
trouble here than you think.

666
00:31:41.833 --> 00:31:44.997
