drew opposite tables.

678
00:32:19.104 --> 00:32:21.649
The only way for him face Berger
is if he beats everyone at his table.

679
00:32:21.673 --> 00:32:23.608
makes it to the
finals. and wins.

680
00:32:29.648 --> 00:32:30.809
Check.

681
00:32:45.564 --> 00:32:46.964
God. must be rough.

682
00:32:48.967 --> 00:32:49.991
Sorry?

683
00:32:50.068 --> 00:32:52.162
