Call.

693
00:33:14.326 --> 00:33:16.727
Ay-ay-ay. action.

694
00:33:16.795 --> 00:33:20.562
Action in my fanny pack.
All right. I'll call you both.

695
00:33:25.036 --> 00:33:27.096
