You think you can
mess with my head. too?

703
00:33:40.585 --> 00:33:41.829
Here's the thing. I'm a psychic.

704
00:33:41.853 --> 00:33:44.288
So if I had to guess.
which I don't. I'd say yes.

705
00:33:44.356 --> 00:33:48.054
Yes. I can mess with your head and I
can put an entire sandwich in your hair.

706
00:33:48.126 --> 00:33:50.166
Well. you know what? I'm
not playing with a psychic.

707
00:33:50.195 --> 00:33:51.527
It's against the rules.

708
00:33:51.596 --> 00:33:54.361
Against the rules? No. guys.
guys. I checked the rulebook.

709
00:33:54.432 --> 00:33:55.991
I looked in the index under "P".

710
00:33:56.067 --> 00:33:59.094
It mentioned polygamy.
pancakes. and pterodactyls.

711
00:33:59.170 --> 00:34:01.105
Who knew pterodactyl
started with a "P"?

712
00:34:01.172 --> 00:34:02.936
I bet you did. You did.

713
00:34:03.008 --> 00:34:05.170
It's not against the
rules. Ronnie. It's cool.

714
00:34:05.243 --> 00:34:07.007
No. it's not cool.

715
00:34:07.078 --> 00:34:08.478
Look at your stack. man.

716
00:34:08.547 --> 00:34:10.243
Everything's here.
Everything's here.

717
00:34:10.315 --> 00:34:13.046
I need you here. Take
a risk. man! Bluff it up!

718
00:34:13.919 --> 00:34:15.979
I'll raise you two
hundred thousand.

719
00:34:16.288 --> 00:34:18.917
You just bluffed to prove
to me that you could bluff.

720
00:34:18.990 --> 00:34:21.118
Ronnie...

721
00:34:21.893 --> 00:34:24.920
I call this move the all in.

722
00:34:31.903 --> 00:34:34.304
Ronnie with the origami.

723
00:34:37.842 --> 00:34:39.572
Oh! Oh!

724
00:34:59.164 --> 00:35:00.792
<i>Center table showdown.</i>

725
00:35:00.865 --> 00:35:03.266
<i>Shawn Spencer and J.P. Berger.</i>

726
00:35:30.829 --> 00:35:32.024
